{"word":"G4797 - συγχέω - synchéō - soong-kheh'-o - Confound","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">συγχέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">synchéō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">soong-kheh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Confound</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - கலக்கமடை, அமளியுண்டாக்கு, கலக்கமாயிரு, கலங்கப்பண்ணு"},{"paragraph":"to pour together, commingle"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong></i>Or <b>&#x03C3;&#x03C5;&#x03B3;&#x03C7;&#x03C5;&#x0301;&#x03BD;&#x03C9;</b> <b>sugchuno&#x0304;</b> <i>soong-khoo'-no<p/></i>From <a href=\"#/G4862 - σύν - sýn - soon/4862\">G4862</a> and <b>&#x03C7;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03C9;</b> &ldquo;<b>cheo&#x0304;</b>&rdquo; (to <i>pour</i>) or its alternate; to <i>commingle</i> promiscuously, that is, (figuratively) to <i>throw</i> (an assembly) <i>into disorder</i>, to <i>perplex</i> (the mind): - confound, confuse, stir up, be in an uproar.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}